## ❌⭕ Tic Tac Toe Game – JavaScript Project

A simple and interactive **Tic Tac Toe game**, built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. Play against another player on the same device with a clean UI and smooth gameplay.

🔗 [Live Demo](https://lalkrish2006.github.io/Tic-Tac-Toe/)

---

## 🧠 About the Project

This is a classic **2-player Tic Tac Toe game** implemented entirely on the frontend. It handles game logic, win conditions, draw detection, and board resets — all with clean UI and zero page reloads.

---

## 🎮 Features

- 🎲 Two-player gameplay (X vs O)
- 🧠 Win/draw detection logic
- 🔁 Reset button to play again
- 🖱️ Click-based input with turn tracking
- 📱 Responsive design (playable on mobile)

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

| Tech        | Description                          |
|-------------|--------------------------------------|
| HTML5       | Game board structure                 |
| CSS3        | Styling and layout                   |
| JavaScript  | Game logic and interaction handling  |
| GitHub Pages| Hosting and deployment               |

